Package: ircd-hybrid
Version: 7.0
Revision: 1
Maintainer: Alexander Strange <astrange@ithinksw.com>
ConfigureParams: --enable-select --disable-openssl
Source: ftp://ftp.blackened.com/pub/irc/hybrid/%n-%v.tgz 
Source-MD5: bee69c994c70fb29a711614150587cd4
PatchScript: sed 's:@DSTROOT@:%d/:g' < %a/%n.patch | patch -p1
Description: IRC Server
PreInstallScript: <<
#!/bin/sh
if [ $1 != "upgrade" ]; then
cp -R %p/lib/ircd/ %p/etc/ircd_old/ || true
fi
<<
PostInstallScript: <<
mv %i/etc/example.conf %i/etc/ircd.example.conf
<<
DescPackaging: <<
If you're upgrading from hybrid-v6, your old %p/lib/ircd is backed up to %p/etc/ircd_old, and can be updated with convertconf and convertilines. 
<<
